---
import Image from "astro/components/Image.astro";
import myPhoto from "/public/photo.webp";
const personalImageAlt = "Mikel Echeverria, Backend & Full Stack Engineer";
---

<article
  class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_200px] gap-12 items-start"
>
  <div class="text-pretty order-2 md:order-1">
    <div class="space-y-6 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed text-lg sm:text-xl [&>p>strong]:font-semibold [&>p>strong]:text-zinc-950 dark:[&>p>strong]:text-white">
        <p data-i18n="about.content">
          Soy <strong>Mikel Echeverria</strong>, un <strong>Backend & Full Stack Engineer</strong>. Mi enfoque combina rigor técnico con comunicación efectiva para construir sistemas escalables end-to-end. Además, exploro continuamente la <strong>Inteligencia Artificial</strong> y los <strong>modelos generativos</strong> para desarrollar soluciones robustas que optimicen procesos y aporten valor real.
        </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="order-1 md:order-2 flex justify-center md:justify-end">
    <Image
      width="200"
      height="200"
      src={myPhoto}
      alt={personalImageAlt}
      class="w-48 h-48 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-sm ring-1 ring-zinc-200 dark:ring-zinc-800 transition-transform duration-500 hover:scale-[1.03]"
    />
  </div>
</article>
